5000|$|Maille {{was sold}} to Paribas Affaires Industrielles in 1997. It was bought by Unilever in 2000. In 2011 new {{products}} were introduced: a <b>Dijon</b> <b>mustard</b> with Chablis [...] "1747", an aged balsamic vinegar and black truffle mustard.|$|R
